title: Toyland
description: A nursery frieze printed in a long narrow format. Contains children's toys, including, from left to right, a train, 2 dolls, sailboats, giraffe, blocks, a rocking horse, teddy bear and a duck with umbrella. Two floral sprigs tied with a bow knot are interspersed. A ribbon band runs along the top and bottom edges. Printed in pink and blue.
name: Frieze
